00:00:12.960 --> 00:00:15.630
is because you end up with a, a

00:00:15.630 --> 00:00:19.020
deletion that causes a premature stop codon, because

00:00:19.020 --> 00:00:21.500
we end up with this huge frame shift

00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:25.380
in the letters. For the rest of the sequence.

00:00:25.380 --> 00:00:29.750
