00:00:32.259 --> 00:00:34.810
out to like a thousand in this gene. So at this

00:00:34.810 --> 00:00:37.260
very early position, we've got a stop code on, so we're

00:00:37.260 --> 00:00:41.160
going to end up with a much shorter protein overall. So take

